{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idef248fe4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2008b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2008b"},"text":"§ 2008b.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Socially disadvantaged farmers and ranchers; qualified beginning farmers and ranchers","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In the case of a loan guaranteed by the Secretary under subchapter I or II to a socially disadvantaged farmer or rancher (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2003/e"},"text":"section 2003(e) of this title","children":[],"tail":") or a qualified beginning farmer or rancher, the Secretary may provide for a standard guarantee plan, which shall cover an amount equal to 95 percent of the outstanding principal of the loan."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idef248fe5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128/tIII/s367"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128, title III, § 367","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/tV/s5306"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, title V, § 5306","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/4673"},"text":"132 Stat. 4673","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idef248fe6-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idef248fe7-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idef248fe8-3a6e-11f1-